name: Olivia
description:
Olivia is a beautiful glass piece. You can dress her up however you like. She loves to go lots of places in your home. It's up to you where you put her and I'm sure she'll be beautiful wherever you choose.

Enjoy and have fun!

Delia Dahlia

Pictured, Olivia just loves holding your potions and powders in a graceful way!
